{"tid":1364103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真野］猶豫既人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:00:43.000Z","uid":143514,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fde99e78c245f09c5eb1bcf695f3e161d072102f","tid":1364103,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"首先 <br />\n咩叫抗爭 抗爭就係面對不公 而挺身而出<br />\n依家眾所週知警黑勾結 政治失陷 所以我地反對 我地抗議<br />\n<br />\n黑警反對通知書咁又點 睇番之前有反對書同冇反對書咪一樣 一樣有人被捕 被打 <br />\n<br />\n咁點解面對不公我地要驚 仲要受制於一個腐敗政府<br />\n記住我地係自由人 我地係新時代既人 我地唔再要舊有既框架而局限我地 <br />\n<br />\n勇武既繼續勇武 和理非盡快覺悟 唔好再信政府會為我地改變 因為要改 5年前一早改左<br />\n<br />\n 我地唔應該被局限 唔應該自己準備好 但人地未準備好而唔去做<br />\n<br />\n所以 光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n727點都要去"},{"pid":"c0ee3e22b3e7dc98141e5cbabe161cb5778aba93","tid":1364103,"uid":143514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"ec004dace90b8696f270a4c4a5b83d1e9820cd2a","tid":1364103,"uid":171504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:41:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾港府回氣！<br />\n<br />\n新死線！<br />\n<br />\n【記住條formula】死線已定，728不排除升級！置頂！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363572</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n726 5點 交代上環元朗 針對黑警<br />\n728 2點 回應五大訴求 針對政權<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/70hg0QQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F70hg0QQ.jpg&h=5f3b0a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NEtPBpe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNEtPBpe.jpg&h=d22be929&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vuBph.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vuBph.jpg&h=f992e9fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5e7ec9b4c3d66b3ed82d8c749c0bfa431d9d225","tid":1364103,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09